\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b1\i0\cf5 Setting:<!$Scr_Ps::2><$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 - Location:}{\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::5> Riverwalk Naperville, Illinois. The Naperville Riverwalk, often referred to as the "crown jewel" of Naperville, Illinois, presents a picturesque setting that winds along the DuPage River. It is a favorite spot for locals and visitors alike, offering a serene and beautiful backdrop for a leisurely stroll or a romantic walk. The Riverwalk features beautifully landscaped paths, charming bridges, and ornate fountains, creating a tranquil environment amidst the bustling city. Along the way, there are ample benches for sitting and enjoying the natural beauty, as well as sculptures and artwork that add a cultural touch to the experience. The Riverwalk also hosts a variety of amenities, including an outdoor amphitheater for public events, a children's playground, and the historic Centennial Beach, turning the area into a lively hub of activity.<!$Scr_Cs::5>}
